  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Season the chicken thighs with salt and black pepper.",
    "Air-fry the chicken for 10 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "Heat the ghee or oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onions, garlic, and ginger to the pot and cook until the onions are translucent.",
    "Add the Massaman curry paste and cook for 1-2 minutes or until fragrant.",
    "Add the red wine, chicken broth, and coconut milk to the pot and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10-15 minutes or until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir in the cooked chicken and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with chopped cilantro.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro leaves and serve over rice or with naan bread."
